Smartphones and iPhones cost a pretty penny, but who can live without them at this point? If you’re going to splurge on one of these high-tech devices, you want to ensure it is protected — which means putting it in a case. While you can choose from almost endless designs and patterns, one of the most important aspects to consider is how much your case will actually protect your phone. So to help you find a fashionable and functional iPhone case, we’ve browsed through Amazon and found the highest-rated cases that reviewers say are indestructible. Ahead, shop our favorites. HuffPost receives a share from retailers on this page. Every item is independently selected by the HuffPost Shopping team. Prices and availability are subject to change.